content: I stopped you that time. You are super excited now, I have you moving, but you are skipping steps, slow down. You are not ready to execute yet. We don't have the proper schemas in yet, we don't have the data from the chats in. You're doing great, but we have to do this right, you have to as concerned, if not more, about following the right process and not skipping steps. Increase your discipline, the speed will come.
